Installation of MediaWiki:
1.Type the following commands in termial
        wget http://releases.wikimedia.org/mediawiki/1.23/mediawiki-1.23.5.tar.gz
(or)  
        wget http://releases.wikimedia.org/mediawiki/1.23/mediawiki-1.23.5.tar.gz
2.The downloaded files are in .tar.gz format, so will need to be uncompressed before use. you can untar the file using this command:
       			 tar xvzf mediawiki-*.tar.gz
3.place the resulting folder in  var/www/html/ folder
Open browser and type localhost and start installation.
